HEADWORD: Intinctivity
<hw>In`tinc*tiv"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + L. <ets>tinctus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>tingere</ets>
to tinge]</ety> <def>The lack of the quality of coloring or tingeing
